---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Work - Emmanuel Gutierrez Pizarro">

  <!-- ENGLISH -->
  <div class="lang-en">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="page-header">
        <h1>Work</h1>
        <p>A selection of projects that reflect the breadth of the territorial, financial and community work I lead through JP Asesores.</p>
      </div>
      <section class="projects">
        <div class="project-list">
          <div class="project-item"><div class="project-year">2026</div><div class="project-info"><h3>Business & Financial Plan, Asocove Dos Rios de Upala</h3><p>Business plan, financial plan, model and annexes for a rural community project. Replicable work in social and solidarity economy contexts.</p><div class="project-tags"><span class="tag tag-model">Financial model</span></div></div></div>
          <div class="project-item"><div class="project-year">2024</div><div class="project-info"><h3>Nosara Community Census</h3><p>Coordination of the first district-level census in Costa Rica, with technical advisory from the National Institute of Statistics and Census (INEC). 95.1% household coverage. USD 120,000 raised plus USD 50,000 in-kind.</p><div class="project-tags"><span class="tag tag-data">Data</span><span class="tag tag-fiscal">Fiscal</span><span class="tag tag-funds">Funds</span></div></div></div>
          <div class="project-item"><div class="project-year">2024</div><div class="project-info"><h3>Nosara District Territorial Fiscal Balance</h3><p>First district-level fiscal study in Costa Rica. Fiscal gap quantified (above USD 55M per year), cadastral gap factor (12.1x), 96.6% informal lodging identified. Estimated district GDP: USD 2.13 billion.</p><div class="project-tags"><span class="tag tag-fiscal">Fiscal</span><span class="tag tag-data">Data</span></div></div></div>
          <div class="project-item"><div class="project-year">2024 - now</div><div class="project-info"><h3>Operating Systems for Territorial Intelligence</h3><p>Territorial intelligence framework integrating fiscal analysis, census data and participatory governance. Includes the Mapa de Voces de Nosara, a weighted-distribution governance model with four representation sectors. First field deployment: the district of Nosara.</p><div class="project-tags"><span class="tag tag-data">Data</span><span class="tag tag-fiscal">Fiscal</span></div></div></div>
          <div class="project-item"><div class="project-year">2013 - 2020</div><div class="project-info"><h3>Entrepreneurship, innovation &amp; early-stage support</h3><p>13 years of experience in entrepreneurship, innovation and early-stage venture support. Program Coordinator at Yo Emprendedor 2013-2020.</p><div class="project-tags"><span class="tag tag-model">Early-stage</span></div></div></div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- ESPANOL -->
  <div class="lang-es">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="page-header">
        <h1>Proyectos</h1>
        <p>Seleccion de proyectos que reflejan la diversidad del trabajo territorial, financiero y comunitario que realizo desde JP Asesores.</p>
      </div>
      <section class="projects">
        <div class="project-list">
          <div class="project-item"><div class="project-year">2026</div><div class="project-info"><h3>Plan de Negocios y Plan Financiero, Asocove Dos Rios de Upala</h3><p>Elaboracion de plan de negocios, plan financiero, modelo y anexos para proyecto rural comunitario. Trabajo replicable en contextos de economia social y solidaria.</p><div class="project-tags"><span class="tag tag-model">Modelo financiero</span></div></div></div>
          <div class="project-item"><div class="project-year">2024</div><div class="project-info"><h3>Censo Comunitario de Nosara</h3><p>Coordinacion del primer censo a nivel de distrito en Costa Rica, con asesoria tecnica del Instituto Nacional de Estadistica y Censos (INEC). Cobertura del 95.1% de hogares. USD 120,000 en fondos gestionados y USD 50,000 en aportes en especie.</p><div class="project-tags"><span class="tag tag-data">Datos</span><span class="tag tag-fiscal">Fiscal</span><span class="tag tag-funds">Fondos</span></div></div></div>
          <div class="project-item"><div class="project-year">2024</div><div class="project-info"><h3>Balance Fiscal Territorial del Distrito de Nosara</h3><p>Primer estudio fiscal a nivel de distrito en Costa Rica. Cuantificacion de la brecha fiscal (superior a USD 55M anuales), calculo del factor de brecha catastral (12.1x), identificacion de 96.6% de alojamientos informales. PIB estimado del distrito: USD 2.13 mil millones.</p><div class="project-tags"><span class="tag tag-fiscal">Fiscal</span><span class="tag tag-data">Datos</span></div></div></div>
          <div class="project-item"><div class="project-year">2024 - hoy</div><div class="project-info"><h3>Sistemas Operativos para Inteligencia Territorial</h3><p>Framework de inteligencia territorial que integra analisis fiscal, datos censales y gobernanza participativa. Incluye el Mapa de Voces de Nosara, un modelo de distribucion ponderada con cuatro sectores de representacion. Primer despliegue en campo: el distrito de Nosara.</p><div class="project-tags"><span class="tag tag-data">Datos</span><span class="tag tag-fiscal">Fiscal</span></div></div></div>
          <div class="project-item"><div class="project-year">2013 - 2020</div><div class="project-info"><h3>Emprendimiento, innovación y apoyo a proyectos en fase temprana</h3><p>13 años de experiencia en emprendimiento, innovación y apoyo a proyectos en fase temprana. Coordinador de Programas en Yo Emprendedor 2013-2020.</p><div class="project-tags"><span class="tag tag-model">Fase temprana</span></div></div></div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </div>

</Layout>
